312
00:17:48,000 --> 00:17:49,680
We think you're truly talented.

313
00:17:49,680 --> 00:17:51,640
And you have youthful energy.

314
00:17:51,640 --> 00:17:53,720
Plus, you're creative.

315
00:17:54,119 --> 00:17:54,920
Li Zhenggui,

