435
00:25:06,960 --> 00:25:07,759
Cheers to dinner.

436
00:25:07,920 --> 00:25:09,240
Cheers to Li Zhenggui's new job.

437
00:25:15,160 --> 00:25:15,960
Let's eat!

438
00:25:37,160 --> 00:25:38,240
I want to eat rice.

439
00:25:38,880 --> 00:25:40,200
Pumpkin counts as a staple.

440
00:25:41,039 --> 00:25:42,039
I want rice.

441
00:25:43,039 --> 00:25:44,119
Then I want a bowl too.

442
00:28:11,039 --> 00:28:12,839
So our barista—

